OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FReform UK have made sweeping gains
OL,7,Facross the North West, a success
OL,8,Fdescribed by leader Nigel Farage as a
OL,9,F'truly historic shift in British
OL,10,Fpolitics'.
OL,12,FThe party, which only formed in 2021,
OL,13,Fpicked up 99 new seats in the North
OL,14,FWest overnight, including 18 in
OL,15,FTameside, a result which saw Labour's
OL,16,Fmonopoly over the local authority end
OL,17,Fafter 47 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
