CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FSpeaking on Friday morning in
OL,7,FHavering, where Reform had just taken
OL,8,Fmajority control of Havering Borough
OL,9,FCouncil, Nigel Farage said: "Labour
OL,10,Fare being wiped out by Reform in many
OL,11,Fof their traditional areas."
OL,13,FHe said: "If you go to Merseyside and
OL,14,FGreater Manchester, have a look at
OL,15,Fwhat we have achieved overnight
OL,16,Falready in results. Tameside being an
OL,17,Fexample, we won all the seats that
OL,18,Fwere up overnight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
