OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FThe headline grabbing result for
OL,7,FReform came in the early hours of
OL,8,FFriday, as they wrestled full control
OL,9,Fof Tameside Council away from Labour,
OL,10,Fan authority widely seen as a safe,
OL,11,FLabour stronghold.
OL,13,FLabour supporters shed tears as a slew
OL,14,Fof long-serving councillors, including
OL,15,Fdeputy leader Taf Sharif and former
OL,16,Fcouncil leader Brenda Warrington lost
OL,17,Ftheir seats.
OL,19,FTheir despair was in stark contrast to
OL,20,Fthe jubilant scenes in the Reform UK
OL,21,Fcamp at Dukinfield Town Hall
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FSpeaking at the Tameside count, Rob
OL,7,FBarrowcliffe, chair of Tameside Reform
OL,8,FUK told ITV Granada: "It was well
OL,9,Fbeyond my expectations. 18 out of 19's
OL,10,Fnot so bad! It's clear by the result
OL,11,Fthat the people of Tameside are fed
OL,12,Fup, and they're demanding change."
OL,14,F"People just want common sense, they
OL,15,Fwant decency, they want fairness."
OL,17,F"I can tell you, our guys will not let
OL,18,Fthe people of Tameside down."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FIt was a scene mirrored right across
OL,7,Fthe North West, as Reform UK made
OL,8,Fsubstantial gains, performing well in
OL,9,Fevery borough. There is expected to be
OL,10,Frelief within the Labour Party that
OL,11,Fthere were so few all-out elections,
OL,12,Fwith Reform unable to mathematically
OL,13,Ftake control of any councils outright.
OL,15,FChair of Reform Halton branch Jonathan
OL,16,FMackie said the party was already
OL,17,Ftargeting taking control of the
OL,18,Fcouncil next year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FIn the first result of the night,
OL,7,Fdecades of Labour dominance of Halton
OL,8,FCouncil was upended.
OL,10,FReform claimed 16 of 19 available
OL,11,Fseats in the Halton Council elections.
OL,12,FLabour held on to just two of its
OL,13,Fseats.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FMr Mackie said: "We were expecting
OL,7,Fmaybe 14, but to deliver 16 out of 19
OL,8,Fis unbelievable really. The Labour
OL,9,Fvote collapsed everywhere, which is
OL,10,Fnot really a surprise, because we've
OL,11,Fbeen out on the doorstep and it was
OL,12,Fclear that there was a mood for
OL,13,Fchange, and we've delivered."
OL,15,FHe added: "We've got a year ahead
OL,16,Fbecause we're the major opposition
OL,17,Fnow, so we're going to have to hold
OL,18,Fthem to account. But next year, the
OL,19,Fplan is to take control of council."
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@]O]wD@KOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
