PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FThe spread of Reform UK's local
OL,7,Felection wins across the country so
OL,8,Ffar is "highly significant" as a sign
OL,9,Fof potential performance at a future
OL,10,Fgeneral election, a polling expert has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FKeiran Pedley, politics director at
OL,14,FIpsos, noted that Nigel Farage's party
OL,15,Fhad gained council seats across the
OL,16,Fnorth of England and in places
OL,17,Fincluding Dudley, Southampton and
OL,18,FPlymouth.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FHe told the Press Association: "Reform
OL,7,Fhas only been a national party for a
OL,8,Fcouple of years, and so we're always
OL,9,Flooking for evidence that they're the
OL,10,Freal deal in terms of a potential
OL,11,Fgoverning party in the UK.
OL,13,F"I think what we're seeing in these
OL,14,Fresults is because they're winning
OL,15,Fsupport across the country, that is
OL,16,Fthe activist base that forms the
OL,17,Fcampaigning base for when you're
OL,18,Ftrying to win parliamentary seats in a
OL,19,Ffuture general election.
OL,26,@nD@`OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,F"The fact that they are winning
OL,7,Fconvincingly against Labour across the
OL,8,Fnorth of England is highly
OL,9,Fsignificant. But I think what's really
OL,10,Fimportant too is that they're gaining
OL,11,Fnot just there, but across the country
OL,12,Fas well."
OL,14,FOn Friday morning Reform UK Leader
OL,15,FNigel Farage compared the substantial
OL,16,Fgains to clearing Becher's Brook, a
OL,17,Ffamously difficult jump in the Grand
OL,18,FNational.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,F"If we cleared Beecher's Brook and
OL,7,Flanded well, we go on to win the Grand
OL,8,FNational.
OL,10,F"What is very clear to me is that our
OL,11,Fvoters will stick with us now all the
OL,12,Fway through."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
