PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778238120
OL,3,CSweeping gains for Reform UK across
OL,4,Cthe North West as party looks to future
OL,6,FMr Farage said: "What's happened is a
OL,7,Ftruly historic shift in British
OL,8,Fpolitics. We've been so used to
OL,9,Fthinking about politics in terms of
OL,10,Fleft and right, yet what Reform are
OL,11,Fable to do is to win in areas that
OL,12,Fhave always been Conservative, but
OL,13,Fequally, we're proving in a big way
OL,14,Fthat we could win in areas that Labour
OL,15,Fhas dominated since the end of World
OL,16,FWar I.
OL,18,F"It's a big, big day, not just for our
OL,19,Fparty, but for a complete reshaping of
OL,20,FBritish politics in every way."
OL,26,@nD@QOUzD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
